node.text:
Anticipating the launch of Aquazzura Casa, we’re delighted to announce our first collaboration with Officine Gullo creating a tailor-made kitchen for Aquazzura. 
The kitchen, painted in iconic Aqua color, fits perfectly into the environment, characterized by a striped painted parquet floor and hand decorated walls. Exotic animals, flowers and brightly colored trees lead the observer to an exotic garden.
@edgardoaquazzura  @officine_gullo 
#AQUAZZURA #officinegullo #madeinitaly
